eu.fbk.dkm.springles

Class Factory.Provider<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • eu.fbk.dkm.springles.Factory.Provider<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - the type of objects produced by the provider.
    Enclosing class:
    Factory<T>

    private static final class Factory.Provider<T>
extends Object
    A provider entry in the registry of registered providers.

    This helper class contains the metadata associated to a provider, namely its URI, the type of produced object and the reflection object for the factory-creation method.
